Well i think like half of the high school population i am in love with the idea of being mrs.darcy...oh it was an amazing movie...proabably would have been better if there hadnt been all of those "great" people making comments and shouting, talking on their cell phones,etc.  By the by it was the most amazing Romance movie i have ever seen.  Love the genius that came up with that ending.  Incredible.  Best part was of course the rain scene and uhhhhhhhhh the fog scene.  Honestly why can guys not be that way anymore.  There seems to be no romance left in the world.  No heart felt romance.  Oh to live in that surreality.  I would be in heaven.  I think half of the people didnt respect that movie partly because they have not read that book.. This is one movie that does the book justice..and that is a hard to find quality in hollywood productions today.  By the way if you don't already know they are filming some scenes to the prequel of "The Texas Chainsaw Massacre" right down the street.   LOL in Martindale of all places.  Well it is pretty late and i need some sleep so for now i will talk to yall later.  Free Refills anyone? :D im bored
Good night und schalft gut.
Kye

i saw myself in the mirror. i saw what i wanted.  what it might be like.  i wanted it more.  but then the realization was that it was just a reflection and nothing more.  maybe you are right and what we want will happen if we stick to it long enough.  oh how i have stuck to it.  probably will for quite a long time.  anything is possible, even me being happy.  this happy thing sounds kinda nice maybe i will try it.

I wish some people would update more....  I miss them.  So nothing out of the ordinary.  School sucks, schiflett isn't the nicest person.  Art project damn stippiling.  Newsflash... B/C i can not cut straight every time i am therefore not perfect my bad :D oh i wish i could take everything with a grain of salt it just depends on your mood.  I did a wopping 1 minute speech today.  It was easy.  During art class today i got called out to go to the office.. i was scared they where going to yell at me for parking next to bowie bc i dont have the truck that is registered to my parking spot but it just turns out that i am one of the Lion Clubs "Student of the Week" and i am very confused.  I am hungry.  I want to be a pirate :( ;) life ahhhhahahahhaha my german wrote me an email today.  I miss her and the other germans.  O my mom is home that might mean food so i think i will go and try to do some homework haha fat chance.  :D

You know I never thought it would be this hard to host a exchange student.  It sounds stupid but it is alot of stress.  Last night at Michaels party some peeps and me were talking about it and it is like having a child to take care of.  On the topic of Michaels party it was pretty good.  Just chillin basically and enjoying some amazing lasagna and cheescake.  Found out that Elfie and Astrid are crazy. Weeee Armadillo's.  Skippy fell and hurt himself in an attempt to scare Susan and I.. To say the least it was pretty hilarious. We also went to Gruene that day too.  It was good I think the Germans had fun and all.  We went to the Outlet Malls after and i "accesorized" :D That made me happy.  Today we went and ate at Hong Kong.  Lecker! I saw about 5 peeps from school at H-E-B.  Such a small town lol.  anyhow Caitlyns "welcome party" went well.  We swam and hung out at the river.  I got a stone bruise on the ball of my foot but that did not stop me from jumping on the trampoline :D School still sucks.. It is the "debby downer" of my life.  That and stupid people that think that having a gf is the only thing that matters and no matter how long they have been involved in somthing they can put it off until the last second and excpect everyone to be ok with it.  Hell no is all i have to say.  That and couples in general make me sad....I am so lonely it isnt even funny.  Yes I have friends and a german that i love but you know just that some you can kiss and hug and just be with is missing from my life.  Speaking of my german she is crazy but a good kind of crazy. :d She does her stretches and makes all these weird noises lol.  and she was playing with the vaccum lol she is crazy!  Well i guess i dont blame her..i subjected her to Napoleon Dynamite today while everyone went bowling...good times.  Well for now thats it i am kinda tired. 

Ciao
Kye

Well I thought that I would take this time out of my day to rant and rave.  I must for my own self.  I keep everything built up inside and although I may hint that somthing is wrong I never express it.  Its time to let loose and even if I sound stupid in the process I will hopefully feel better.       So of course now I am the utmost alone.  Its sad and there isnt anything it seems that I can do.  I see people who are happier than I and they all seem to be in a nice functional relationship.  What is it about me that makes me so relationship incapable?  And also what is with that fact that the only people that I ever seem to want are people already with someone else?  It doesnt seem fair that that well I dont know.  It isnt fair that others can have their way when it seems that no matter what I am inevitaly doomed to seldomly see things go my way.  Now that I am thinking about it I happend to stumble upon an old memory.  Well it will be about a year old in November but still.  It seems like such a long time ago that for a split second in my life things might have actually gone my way.  I wonder what happend to make it happen and what happend to make it end.  Its sad because what ever caused it to end is still haunting me today to this very second.  I seem so touchy when it comes to this subject.  I was told to wait it out.  To be the invisible girl and then one day be the girl who takes their breath away.  Maybe it will happen maybe it wont, but oh how I want it to.  It seems that I live for this.  I cannot imagine my crumy life with out the thing that makes me crum.  It so sad yet so hard to give up the thing that I love so much.  One day yes maybe one day I will conquer it and be like "haha I have conquered you" but no that seems so unreasonable.     Another thing, when ever I am around people that I am not totally comfortable with ,such a people that I think think they are better than me, I feel so out of place.  I feel like I may be trying to hard to fit in and be one of them when in reality I want to be myself but be excepted for who I am but that doesnt look like it is going to happen either.  Im not trying to hard Im just there :(  It doesnt help that half of those people intimidate me.    And another big problem to my screwed up and disfunctional life are my brothers.  Now it is mainly my stupid and imature younger brother who lives with me but this weekend it was both.  I went and visited my older brother,his wife and their new child.  Now my god he is 30, has a kid, and STILL treats me like shit.  I hate it.  Almost as much as I hate the crap my younger brother pulls.  I am constantly fed up with him and then he goes and has a bad day and expects me to give him a damn ounce of respect when he never even thinks about doing it for me! I just hate that shit.  Well for now thats it.  Other than school but I wont even go there..........ohhhhhhhhh...... ok whatever im out for the count....1....2.....3...a....b....c......Kye

Mwahahahaha.  Peace out homies.

I need your arms around me i need to feel your touch.....i need your understanding i need your love so much..you tell me that you love me so you tell me that you care but when i need you your never there...always threw such strong resistance first you say your to busy i wonder if you even miss me...your never there.......never ever there.....a golden bird that flies away a candles fickle flame to think i held you yesterday your love was just a game...take the time to get know me if you want me why cant you just show me..we are always on this rollercoaster..your never there


you turn the screws you tear down the bridge flimsy as it is its buisness like ..you shake my hand you break up the band its open mic ...you twist the knife  then go home and kiss your wife a bigger better slice is what you like..you kick the sand you  get the upper hand you sell it to japan...you turn the screws its what you choose to do you think that i turn them too...you think that i must be so satisfyed lets stay inside i wonder why..and the cement mixer gets it all ready one good turn at a time then pouring it slowly and steady your showing me where to sign what i can ecxpect to find but how can you be happy when you turn the screws?  you turn the screws its what you choose to do..you think that i must turn them too...flimsy as it is...

im not feeling that fine today im not feeling alright

Its amazing and almost spirit lifting to know that someone half way around the world actually cares...*sniff i love my german she is great. So Far Birthday presents 3...lets see how the day progresses:D i have to be happy today its a pretty good start           ~Kye

So last night at around midnight my older brother calls us to tell us that tami( his wife) is in labor.  Its pretty amazing that life works this way.  There are some things in life that are sacred, for my brother and tami this is one.  The major life changer, from now on they will always have this little "critter" to look after.  And i hope it goes well.  And then of course there are other things in life that are sacred and not meant to be openly shared with the world.  And in turn that kinda makes life complicated.  But no one can really change that but anyhow tomorrow is (as props movers) our first real day of practice.  EXCITING! not well its all good i guess.  I gotta go Hong Kong is calling my name yummy:D

One of the most talked about topics is one that is on my mind all the time now.  America it seems may be falling.  I dont know maybe it is kinda dumb to think that, but it sure doesnt seem to be getting better.  First and foremost, the hurrican katrina that hit louisianna has caused a ripple affect all over the south, and also the fact that it isnt the last one is even worse.  the fact that people are dying in masses and that it will take years to restore and even get help is outrageous.  Now i know that we can't all blame bush for everything even though it may be partly his fault for not listening, but omg what is his deal?  My mom and her friend where thinking about going to louisianna to help but they decided not too bc of all the looters and all the chaos and such.  I want to help out as much as i can so i donated all i had and ask that yall wil consider doing the same. pitching in to the local orginizations that are going to send money to the red cross or something would be one of the best things for our country today. On another note gas prices are ridiculous, yet another ripple felt by the entire coninent of the USA.  Its completly bonkers.  they say prices will go up to $4 on monday and i know, like the majority of the peeps out there cant afford to drive anywhere anymore.  I want a hybrid car.  my birthday is soon but that doesnt matter.  On a lighter note my mom got me a awesome ring today for a early birthday present.  Its an eastern star.  My greatgrandmother was a part of that orginization its cool. well i gotta go figure out whats gunna go down.

And then i usually find myself once again hoplessly taking quizzes on quizzila.com wishing for a good outcome.I mean honsetly, one quiz says im a "loner artist" the other says im the " perfect girlfrind" which is sad because i wouldnt know!*tear o well life seems to go on though  one day it will stop but i hope it doesnt come to that any time soon. But then again you see the good times even though they are limited.  Its too hot to go horseback riding and that upsets me, i cant wait until the fall. So my family will probably head out to california to "celebrate" the critter but that probably means no coldplay concert, o well it cost to much anyhow, hey you know that good feeling you get when you let your hair down after it has been in a pony tail for so long, yea i made some scrumpcious things this night, they were yummy. Lecker!hmmmm i am a true virgo, nice to know, this is what this one quizzy thing told me,,,,, true love comes from a scorpio, capricorn, taurus, your own virgo, and sometimes aquarius.hmmmmm oy ve i will have a hard time falling asleep tonight. who's damon? i went and worked out today for a long while, yes this is getting random...ahhh im sorry everyone, lol or just those few who read it. im going to write a book.  again.  ok i got what i came for now its time to go and TRY to sleep haha sleep whats that, o shit i have to wrap my leg darn scar "made in Germany" my butt ugh anywho gute nacht
